===Etymology 1===
{{etyl|enm}} ''[[answere#Middle English|answere]]'' from {{etyl|ang}} ''[[andswaru]]'' from ''[[and-#Old English|and-]]'' "back, against" + ''[[swaru#Old English|swaro, swaru]]'' "saying, word". Compare {{ang}} ''[[andwyrde#Old English|andwyrde]]'' "answer", {{ang}} ''[[andcwiss#Old English|andcwiss]]'' "reply".

