====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# A [[response]]; something [[say|said]] or [[do|done]] in [[reaction]] to a [[statement]] or [[question]].
#: ''Her '''answer''' to his proposal was a slap in the face''.
# A [[solution]] to a problem.
#: ''There is no simple '''answer''' to curbing corruption.''
# Reply to an email. ([[reply]])
# {{legal}} A [[document]] filed in response to a [[complaint]], responding to each point raised in the complaint and raising [[counterpoint]]s.

